---
title: Crispy Breadcrumb-Topped Tilapia with Zucchini and Tomato Orzo
description: Tilapia fillets are topped with Parmesan and crispy Italian breadcrumbs for a satisfying crunch to go with this mild fish. The Mediterranean inspiration doesn't stop there: orzo is tossed with zucchini and tomatoes in a light garlicky sauce for a delicious, summery meal.
